# textdomain: mcl_compass
Compass=指南針
Points to the world origin=指嚮世界原點
Compasses are tools which point to the world origin (X@=0, Z@=0) or the spawn point in the Overworld.=指南針是指嚮世界原點（X@=0，Z@=0）或主世界的出生點的工具。
A Compass always points to the world spawn point when the player is in the overworld.  In other dimensions, it spins randomly.=當玩家在主世界時，指南針總是指嚮世界重生點。 在其他維度，它隨機旋轉。
Lodestone Compass=磁石指南針
Points to a lodestone=指嚮磁石
Lodestone compasses resemble regular compasses, but they point to a specific lodestone.=磁石指南針類似於常規指南針，但它們指嚮特定的磁石。
A Lodestone compass can be made from an ordinary compass by using it on a lodestone.  After becoming a lodestone compass, it always points to its linked lodestone, provided that they are in the same dimension.  If not in the same dimension, the lodestone compass spins randomly, similarly to a regular compass when outside the overworld.  A lodestone compass can be relinked with another lodestone.=磁石指南針可以通過在磁石上使用普通指南針製成。 成為磁石羅盤後，它總是指嚮與其相連的磁石，前提是它們處於同一維度。 如果不在同一個維度，磁石羅盤會隨機旋轉，類似於在主世界之外的普通羅盤。 磁石指南針可以與另一個磁石重新鏈接。
